This paper is about improving the training procedure for neural autoregressive models for data completion. The paper focuses on improving the performance of autoregressive models for data completion, which is a task related to generative modeling. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
